        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Promoting Diverse Investment Advisers Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Reserve Board to set goals related to woman-, minority-, or veteran-owned or controlled firms in certain investment management agreements made related to the board's authority in unusual and exigent circumstances.</p>]]></text>
